2 Overview of performance metrics

Metric Reported_by Description
AvC30 Area Mean catches over first 30 projected years
C10 Area Mean catches over the first 10 projected years
C20 Area Mean catches over projected years 11-20
C30 Area Mean catches over projected years 21-30
D10 Stock SSB relative to dynamic B0 after 10 projected yrs
D20 Stock SSB relative to dynamic B0 after 20 projected yrs
D30 Stock SSB relative to dynamic B0 after 30 projected yrs
LD Stock Lowest SSB depletion over the 30 years for which the MP is applied
DNC Stock SSB depletion after 30 years, relative to zero catch scenario
LDNC Stock Lowest SSB depletion over the 30 years for which the MP is applied, relative to zero catch scenario
POF Stock Probability of overfishing (F>FMSY) over the first 30 projected years
POS Stock Probability of overfished state (B<BMSY) over the first 30 projected years
PGK Stock Probability of green Kobe (F>FMSY and B<BMSY) over the first 30 projected years
AAVC Area Percentage average annual variability in catches over the first 30 projected years
